cli_comprehensive_analysis.company_overview: Quantum Computing Inc. (QUBT) is a Virginia-based quantum computing software company focusing on quantum application acceleration through their Qatalyst platform. Founded in 2018, the company provides quantum-ready software tools that bridge conventional computing and quantum processing units including DWave, Rigetti, and IonQ.
